data.name: Citibank Foreign Currency Term Deposit - USD
data.description: Choose from a range of major foreign currencies and see how you can guarantee your returns through a Term Deposit in different currencies.

features.additionalInfo: If your term deposit is for longer than one month, we will send you a notice to remind you when the term of your deposit is coming to an end.

constraints.additionalInfo: Minimum investment is equivalent to AUD $50,000.
Minimum investment is equivalent to AUD $50,000.

eligibility.additionalValue: Must be an Australian resident and/or be available to be identified in Australia when opening the account

eligibility.additionalInfo: Must have a valid email address

fees.name: Early Withdrawal Fee
fees.additionalInfo: 20% of the total amount of interest earned on your term deposit in the period from when your term deposit was opened until the day we process your withdrawal request.
